@FootballTransferApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:7176

### Get All News

GET {{FootballTransferApi_HostAddress}}/api/news
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Test News

POST {{FootballTransferApi_HostAddress}}/api/news
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Liverpool interested in Florian Wirtz",
  "content": "Liverpool are monitoring Florian Wirtz.",
  "source": "BBC Sport",
  "url": "https://bbc.com",
  "publishedAt": "2026-06-16T12:00:00Z"
}

###

### Process Single News - OpenAI Test

POST {{FootballTransferApi_HostAddress}}/api/news/process/7

###

### Process All News

POST {{FootballTransferApi_HostAddress}}/api/news/process-all

###

### Get All News After Processing

GET {{FootballTransferApi_HostAddress}}/api/news
Accept: application/json